          <vc_back_teacher-talk>Repitan esta palabra: <vc_teacher-talk-emphasis_non-ital>lisa</vc_teacher-talk-emphasis_non-ital>.</vc_back_teacher-talk>
          <vc_back_c-hed>Define </vc_back_c-hed>
